title: Las Vegas product Ray Smith out for season with Arizona basketball with second ACL tear
text:
Published By: Las Vegas Sun - Today 
Arizona freshman Ray Smith, a key part of coach Sean Miller's latest recruiting class, will not play this season after tearing his right ACL...
